<template>
  <v-navigation-drawer v-model="localDrawer"></v-navigation-drawer>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "NavDrawer",
  props: {
    drawer: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false,
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      localDrawer: this.drawer,
    };
  },
  watch: {
    localDrawer(newValue) {
      this.$emit("updateMyProp", newValue);
    },
  },
};
</script>
